TITLE: Initializing and Using HashMap in Vala
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the initialization of a HashMap with key-value pairs and shows how to set and get values. It also includes iterations over keys and values, making use of the Gee library for Vala. Key parameters include the use of string keys and integer values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/vala-lang/vala-docs/blob/main/source/developer-guides/gee-samples/03-map-sample.rst#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: vala
CODE:
